{"tid":791203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家香港既大陸人都係垃圾","createTime":"2018-08-23T15:08:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T05:12:31.000Z","uid":30176,"like":124,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"74fcb7445a360917eaf6c50120bf365c7ba3bbba","tid":791203,"uid":30176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:08:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6947475\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6947475&d=RzP3LsgGeiXY4iqKetPgmjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=df9a3d72\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6947475</a><br />\n<br />\n高登好post 必需分享<br />\n<br />\n早排做生意識左個大陸老細，響潮州嚟<br />\n聽講身家大概40億左右 (話多唔多話少唔少)<br />\n<br />\n早兩晚一班生意佬係上水果頭圍埋飲茅台，<br />\n有人問佢：覺得香港怎麼樣？有沒有想過長居香港？<br />\n<br />\n大陸老細：「你瞧我不起阿？想長居香港的大陸人都是垃圾！」<br />\n<br />\n我初初以為佢飲大兩杯發UP瘋，點知又解釋得幾有道理<br />\n以下為要點：<br />\n<br />\n70,80年代來香港的是正常，都是避共產黨<br />\n但現在來香港的都是垃圾，都是來逃避現實<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有錢有才華有能力的大陸人都想去英美歐德澳長居<br />\n貧賤愚笨的大陸人，因為外國去不了，只能去香港<br />\n來到香港就拿香港的福利，一家四口拿四間政府房子，做寄生蟲<br />\n現在香港政府收的大多是這些人，專給他們發香港身分證<br />\n所以在香港看到的大多數大陸人都像沒進化的猴子，基因低劣<br />\n<br />\n香港的房子不是人住，是豬狗住的，<br />\n整個城市規劃就是圈養奴隸，比大陸的新城市差<br />\n<br />\n如果你說環境不同，在我看來有咋不同？<br />\n你去看空氣污染指數，去看你喝的東江水，不都是狗屎嗎？<br />\n<br />\n如果談旅遊，我來香港幹嘛呢？有錢為什麼不去外國呢？<br />\n有山有水有女。什麼自由行阿，都是開給貧下人口／工讀生的。<br />\n<br />\n你說香港買房子保值阿，我說炒房地產的人都是垃圾<br />\n在吹大泡沫，沒實質經濟增長，還要抽真正在做實業的人的血。<br />\n<br />\n總結就係：香港係大陸人既堆填區，只有大陸人中既垃圾先會Dom入嚟。<br />\nBTW 條友唔知係咪睇得破壞之王多，成日話人垃圾"},{"pid":"f59a9cac859999ba02b762d80cfe61a635e91c31","tid":791203,"uid":30176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:08:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f0989c2240500587535fc35fa8856b6a9b01b51","tid":791203,"uid":30176,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:09:42.000Z","msg":"你說香港買房子保值阿，我說炒房地產的人都是垃圾<br />\n在吹大泡沫，沒實質經濟增長，還要抽真正在做實業的人的血。<br />\n<br />\n事實 <br />\n香港呢一刻重有咩實業<br />\n炒股炒樓 定倫敦金"},{"pid":"8beb24a9647891a77a68b6a00e56f71e59a1e7c2","tid":791203,"uid":2419,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:09:47.000Z","msg":"大陸人=垃圾"},{"pid":"611d068535d5b50eaf62174f7825dbeea0819039","tid":791203,"uid":30176,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:10:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80360470489c053d2d4a9c7fb67013eb528c01ec","tid":791203,"uid":30176,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:10:30.000Z","msg":"想多啲人睇到"},{"pid":"11e1b7ae8629da383a448d35f8297ff772c19ad5","tid":791203,"uid":30176,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:11:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f83f142552163b75cbc2105bc34b60a8a176424c","tid":791203,"uid":30176,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:12:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f551fb9abed9df74134eac985f75dec2ac69791","tid":791203,"uid":155077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:16:53.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"1b6e43bea757a1236b489bbedba2107b83247d6a","tid":791203,"uid":59014,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:23:19.000Z","msg":"大陸有錢班人去晒澳加美，香港人諗緊既野 大陸人一樣諗緊(想R外國著數 做外國人)<br />\n<br />\n窮個班先要去香港 呢樣好真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"580f650afca73da5d4fe2873f8cc41d1408f819b","tid":791203,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:31:22.000Z","msg":"香港門檻低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a9d69a1b5c5f76b6610e3be12ccc78aa99a24e","tid":791203,"uid":10692,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:34:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cab589b4c6420bb37bbf5f55b1665edfb192e370","tid":791203,"uid":9732,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:35:22.000Z","msg":"而家，以前，以後都係垃圾"},{"pid":"fea48f6d50632f755ade7c56d03fdaedcf4561e2","tid":791203,"uid":80814,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:41:33.000Z","msg":"唔使分咁細喇，都係垃圾，<br />\n有無錢走到嘅分別啫"},{"pid":"aa8f66ee94b845e1d93e9c08b4c35adc288d1409","tid":791203,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:41:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26bcdf543409023069183255de79f3fb0989eb2e","tid":791203,"uid":179938,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:44:02.000Z","msg":"而家香港既人都係垃圾"},{"pid":"7262c685f2432d0da982cf8d87912a4ddde9c65c","tid":791203,"uid":30176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:05:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2d8d6c090adad399c3d78f447ffb77f80b9cd9d2","tid":791203,"uid":30176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:05:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8ba3375870f6afe508ec2dccd472d7ccaecca195","tid":791203,"uid":132524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:07:38.000Z","msg":"講得幾好認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf06ab07f8934021df88dfbf9d69eeaa98d4cf0f","tid":791203,"uid":38523,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:09:46.000Z","msg":"冇個班大陸人來<br />\n香港真係唔錯<br />\n依加樓貴又細就係因為有班大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港本身好好<br />\n屋細唔係問<br />\n東京一樣屋細<br />\n但人地冇殖民<br />\n所以所有問題都係大陸人"},{"pid":"25a22cbc42a4b2b35ad8447e51e18a9cad10d36c","tid":791203,"uid":38523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:11:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><del>而家香港既</del>大陸人都係垃圾</span></span>"},{"pid":"97f0d1a987317dd5a65ad119fd7f515e47a661c8","tid":791203,"uid":201464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"有時話高登高質過連登唔係吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd73736d8321c42f5f536c110398e5023042e3d1","tid":